<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contribute - <%= data.name %></title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif; }
        .gradient-text {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #000000, #333333);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
        }
        /* Styling untuk nomor langkah besar sebagai pengganti ikon */
        .big-number {
            @apply text-8xl font-bold text-neutral-50 absolute -top-10 -left-6 -z-10 select-none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-white text-neutral-900 antialiased leading-relaxed">

    <nav class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 flex items-center justify-between px-6 md:px-24 lg:px-32 h-20 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-neutral-100">
        <a href="/" class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight">
            <%= data.name %><span class="text-neutral-400">.</span>
        </a>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-8 text-sm font-medium">
            <a href="/docs" class="text-neutral-600 hover:text-black transition-colors">Docs</a>
            <a href="/contribute" class="text-black border-b-2 border-black pb-1">Contribute</a>
            <a href="<%= data.repoLink %>" target="_blank" class="bg-black text-white px-5 py-2 hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors">
                GitHub
            </a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="pt-40 pb-24 px-6 md:px-24 lg:px-32 border-b border-neutral-100">
        <div class="max-w-4xl">
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-neutral-400 mb-6 tracking-wide uppercase">
                Join the Community
            </p>
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8 gradient-text">
                Built together, <br> for science.
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-neutral-700 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
                The goal of this project is to create a programming language <strong>together</strong>. Jackal is built by and for open source scientists and developers who want to learn, contribute, and shape the future of a language collaboratively.
            </p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="py-32 px-6 md:px-24 lg:px-32 bg-neutral-50">
        <div class="max-w-4xl">
            <h2 class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500 mb-16 font-bold border-l-4 border-black pl-4">
                Ways to Contribute
            </h2>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
                <div class="group">
                    <div class="h-1 w-12 bg-neutral-200 group-hover:bg-black transition-colors mb-6"></div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Report Bugs</h3>
                    <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
                        Found something broken? Open a detailed issue on GitHub to help us squash it.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="group">
                    <div class="h-1 w-12 bg-neutral-200 group-hover:bg-black transition-colors mb-6"></div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Improve Docs</h3>
                    <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
                        Documentation is vital. Help us make it clearer, fix typos, or add new examples.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="group">
                    <div class="h-1 w-12 bg-neutral-200 group-hover:bg-black transition-colors mb-6"></div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Write Code</h3>
                    <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
                        Ready to dive deep? Pick up an open issue or propose a new feature via Pull Request.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-32 px-6 md:px-24 lg:px-32">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-24 text-center">How to Start</h2>
            
            <div class="space-y-32">
                <div class="relative pl-8 border-l border-neutral-200">
                    <span class="big-number">01</span>
                    <div class="relative">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Fork & Clone</h3>
                        <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-6 max-w-xl">
                            Start by forking the Jackal repository to your own GitHub account, then clone it to your local machine to begin working.
                        </p>
                        <div class="bg-[#1a1a1a] text-neutral-200 p-5 rounded-sm overflow-x-auto border-l-4 border-neutral-600">
                            <code class="font-mono text-sm">$ git clone https://github.com/alegarsio/Jackal-Projects.git</code>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="relative pl-8 border-l border-neutral-200">
                    <span class="big-number">02</span>
                    <div class="relative">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Create a Branch</h3>
                        <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-6 max-w-xl">
                            Never work directly on <code>main</code>. Create a new branch for your specific feature or fix.
                        </p>
                        <div class="bg-[#1a1a1a] text-neutral-200 p-5 rounded-sm overflow-x-auto border-l-4 border-neutral-600">
                            <code class="font-mono text-sm">$ git checkout -b feature/my-awesome-feature</code>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="relative pl-8 border-l border-neutral-200">
                    <span class="big-number">03</span>
                    <div class="relative">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Push & PR</h3>
                        <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-8 max-w-xl">
                            Once you're happy with your changes and tests pass, push your branch and open a Pull Request on the main repository.
                        </p>
                        <a href="<%= data.repoLink %>/pulls" target="_blank" class="bg-black text-white px-8 py-4 font-medium hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors inline-block">
                            Open Pull Request
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="py-16 px-6 text-center border-t border-neutral-100 bg-neutral-50">
        <p class="text-neutral-400 text-xs tracking-wider font-mono">
            Jackal Language Project &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %>. Open Source for Open Scientists.
        </p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>